        "other_details": {
          "en": {
            "provenance": "translation_service",
            "value": "To the Election Officer, I participated in the movement to bring multi-party democracy in 1989. After the establishment of multi-party system, I actively supported various parties and their leaders. However, due to the parties and leaders only fulfilling their personal interests, I wish to be an independent candidate in the upcoming election."
          },
          "ne": {
            "provenance": "imported",
            "value": "श्री निर्वाचन अधिकृत ज्यू मैले बहुदलीय प्रजातन्त्र ल्याउने आन्दोलनमा २०४६ सालमै सहभागी भई बहुदल आइसकेपछि विभिन्न दल र पार्टीका नेतृत्वहरुलाई सकृय सहयोग गर्दै आएकोमा दल र नेतृत्व बाट निजि स्वार्थ मात्र पूरा गरेको कारण आगामी चुनावमा आफै स्वतन्त्र उम्मेदवार हुने इच्छा राखेको छु ।"
          }
        },
